comment.text: This translation key is used to display "Plugin samples" as a heading in the developer tools section of the Portal Settings page. It appears as a bold title above a list of plugin SDK-related content when the user clicks on a link or navigates to this page.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'عينات الاضافات' while understandable, isn't the most natural or precise translation of "Plugin samples". 'عينات' (ayyinat) means 'samples', but 'الاضافات' (al-idaafaat) translates to 'the additions' which is close but not exactly 'plugins'. A more accurate translation might use a term that specifically refers to plugins.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider using 'نماذج الإضافات' (namazij al-idaafaat) which translates to 'Plugin Models/Examples' or 'عينات المكونات الإضافية' (ayyinat al-mukawwinat al-idaafiyya) - 'Samples of Additional Components'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: Missing period at the end of the sentence.

While 'Laajennusmallit' is a possible translation, 'Plugin samples' generally refers to example plugins, not just extensions/add-ons in general. A more accurate translation could consider the context of 'samples' as example implementations.

While 'Exemple de plugin-uri' is understandable, a more natural and accurate translation of 'Plugin samples' would be 'Mostre de plugin-uri' or 'Plugin-uri de exemplu'. 'Exemple' refers to examples in a broader sense, while 'samples' implies a representative selection.

The translation 'ආදර්ශ පේනු' doesn't accurately convey the meaning of 'Plugin samples'. 'ආදර්ශ' means 'model' or 'example,' and 'පේනු' is a less common word for 'plugins'. A more accurate translation would focus on conveying 'examples' or 'sample' plugins, potentially using a phrasing closer to 'ප්ලගින් උදාහරණ' or 'ප්ලගින් నమూనా'.
While 'පේනු' isn't strictly incorrect, it's not the most common or preferred word for 'plugins' in Sinhala in this context. It can be perceived as slightly unnatural.

While "Узорци додатака" is understandable, a more accurate and idiomatic translation of "Plugin samples" would be "Примери додатка/а". "Узорци" implies patterns or designs, which isn't the intended meaning.
